data.description: Country living at its best!   The land is adorned with mature oak trees and olive trees, 18.91 acres of flat usable land.  This property is self-sustainable; with paid-off Solar System and 3 Tesla back-up batteries, 2 working and producing water wells, propane and septic. The property is fenced and cross-fenced with many enclosures for horses and cattle.  There is a large barn with 4 horse stalls, feed storage shed, and other sheds throughout the property.  The possibilities for this property are endless, can also be used to plant a vineyard or other crops.  You have the sound of nature around you, beautiful and colorful birds singing and chickens running around, plenty of room for all your ideas, just bring your imagination to paint the picture of your future home. The house has a pool and spa, 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, large kitchen with newer cabinets and countertops, two fireplaces, tiled flooring and carpet in the bedrooms.  This home is easily accessible right off Highway 94.
